game_name: Brawl Stars - Showdown (Every Brawler for themselves!)
grade_reason: The player consistently made poor engagement decisions, took unnecessary damage, and failed to prioritize healing and positioning, leading to multiple eliminations in a short match.

The player demonstrated strong recovery and excellent late-game execution, effectively utilizing Nita's Super and bear. However, an early game positioning mistake led to an unnecessary 2v1 engagement and significant health loss, which could have been avoided.
The player was eliminated very early in the match due to poor engagement choices and a lack of awareness of opponent power levels. There was minimal offensive action or strategic movement.
